Class User

  • java.lang.Object
    • User

  • public class User
extends java.lang.Object
    User Provides methods and attributes for interacting with users, which are entries representing events stored in the current user accounts file.
    Author:
    Jonathan Gillett, Daniel Smullen, Rayan Alfaheid
